 animals this suggests that there may be universal laws that explain how all forms of life respond to environmental change tags agriculture & aquaculture bacteria biodiversity climate change ecosystem functioning evolution land use microbe sustainability 2012 leopold leadership program the stanford woods institute for the environment stanford university stanford ca 94305
